# Gorgias Webhook API

- API route lives at `app/api/webhooks/gorgias/route.ts`.
- Only handle POST; return 405 for GET, PUT, DELETE.
- When `message.from_agent === true`, return `{ success: true, ignored: "agent_message" }`.
- Otherwise return `{ success: true, received_event: "<event>" }` (use `event` from payload or default `ticket-message-created`).
- Use typed request/response and catch JSON parse errors with 400 + `{ success: false, error: "Invalid JSON body" }`.
